  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Gray Tie Detective Agency Takes On the Case</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the partner of professionals—Detective Amanda and her assistant—in investigating the mysterious theft of an ancient statuette. Your investigation will begin in collector Gino Grasso's study but will quickly take you far beyond his home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll explore Amsterdam's picturesque canals, gloomy ruins of an ancient castle, and a mysterious chemistry lab. At every turn, you'll encounter clever puzzles, hidden objects, and diverse mini-games that will help uncover the secrets of this case.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/f12a0f45ddc66b0d4e788dbe3ae8d5d5.poster.avif?t=1772657456\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/f12a0f45ddc66b0d4e788dbe3ae8d5d5.webm?t=1772657456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/f12a0f45ddc66b0d4e788dbe3ae8d5d5.mp4?t=1772657456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collector's Edition Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your adventure with exclusive content:<br>• 8 additional locations with new puzzles<br>• 8 unique mini-games<br>• A collection of desktop wallpapers<br>• Original soundtracks<br>• Exclusive achievements<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/9fb11c591c81431ba690f28ceee6495c.poster.avif?t=1772657456\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/9fb11c591c81431ba690f28ceee6495c.webm?t=1772657456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/9fb11c591c81431ba690f28ceee6495c.mp4?t=1772657456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join the investigation and become part of this thrilling story!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The investigation will lead you to unexpected discoveries and dangerous confrontations. When the mystery is solved and the criminal brought to justice, you'll receive a well-deserved reward: a ceremonial awards ceremony at the detective agency and recognition of your professional merits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Gray Tie Detective Agency Takes On the Case</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the partner of professionals—Detective Amanda and her assistant—in investigating the mysterious theft of an ancient statuette. Your investigation will begin in collector Gino Grasso's study but will quickly take you far beyond his home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll explore Amsterdam's picturesque canals, gloomy ruins of an ancient castle, and a mysterious chemistry lab. At every turn, you'll encounter clever puzzles, hidden objects, and diverse mini-games that will help uncover the secrets of this case.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/f12a0f45ddc66b0d4e788dbe3ae8d5d5.poster.avif?t=1772657456\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/f12a0f45ddc66b0d4e788dbe3ae8d5d5.webm?t=1772657456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/f12a0f45ddc66b0d4e788dbe3ae8d5d5.mp4?t=1772657456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collector's Edition Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your adventure with exclusive content:<br>• 8 additional locations with new puzzles<br>• 8 unique mini-games<br>• A collection of desktop wallpapers<br>• Original soundtracks<br>• Exclusive achievements<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/9fb11c591c81431ba690f28ceee6495c.poster.avif?t=1772657456\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/9fb11c591c81431ba690f28ceee6495c.webm?t=1772657456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179350/extras/9fb11c591c81431ba690f28ceee6495c.mp4?t=1772657456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join the investigation and become part of this thrilling story!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The investigation will lead you to unexpected discoveries and dangerous confrontations. When the mystery is solved and the criminal brought to justice, you'll receive a well-deserved reward: a ceremonial awards ceremony at the detective agency and recognition of your professional merits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
